conky-mpd
=========

Small conky setup that displays the current playing song info and cover art on the desktop. It fetches the covers from Last.fm.
conkyrc-mpd is based on the "Conky panel and MPD cover art" by SuNjACk94 (see http://sunjack94.deviantart.com/gallery/#/d2jvuuh)
The overlay image is taken from the covergloobus project, theme LucidDark.

Please change the APIKEY variable in cover.sh to your own API key.

The CoverGloobus project is licensed under the GPLv3 License, see the COPYING file.
The Conky panel and MPD cover art project is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution NonCommercial 3.0 Unported license, see http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0/.
